description = "Surge Moves are moves that have stronger effects, but cost Orbs. Each Surge Move requires a certain amount of Orbs to be able to use. Surge Moves gain additional effects with every Orb spent above the minimum amount. You can find the Surge Effect of a Move listed in its Details.

For example, a Surge Move might cost 3 Orbs to use, but increase the attack power of the move. Then, for every Orb the user spends above 3, that move would gain some additional power!"
